            , &amp;c.</p>
               <p>Sixth Count, for the like uttering with intention to defraud 
               <persName id="t17720909-26-person361">
                  John
                   Alexander
               <interp inst="t17720909-26-person361" type="surname" value="Alexander"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17720909-26-person361" type="given" value="John"></interp>
